**The Scenario Modeler: A Moment Worth Watching For**

One of the four demo cases features a Tier 2 member, age 55, taking
early retirement with a 30% benefit reduction. The system calculates her
reduced benefit correctly --- and then, without being asked, identifies
that she is just 2 points shy of meeting the Rule of 75. It shows her
that waiting one additional year would eliminate the penalty entirely,
increasing her monthly benefit by approximately 54%.

This is the kind of insight that experienced staff provide today through
personal knowledge. NoUI makes it systematic and automatic, ensuring
every member gets the same level of guidance regardless of which analyst
processes their application.

**Why This Matters Now**

DERP serves the people who serve Denver. Every firefighter, every city
clerk, every parks employee depends on this plan to deliver their
retirement benefit accurately and on time. The systems that support this
mission are aging, and the people who understand them are retiring.

The question is not whether to modernize --- it is how. The traditional
path costs tens of millions, takes years, and fails more often than it
succeeds. NoUI offers a fundamentally different approach: deploy in
weeks, prove value immediately, modernize progressively, and protect
your data absolutely.

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **NoUI is not asking DERP to trust a new system.** It is asking DERP to
  verify one. Every calculation shows its work. Every rule cites its
  source. Every result can be checked by hand. Trust is earned through
  transparency, not promised through marketing.

