2.  **Calculation Audit:** NoUI independently verifies 50--100 real
    member calculations against your current system. This step alone
    often surfaces discrepancies worth investigating.

3.  **Board Presentation:** Present findings and proposal to the board
    of trustees, addressing fiduciary concerns directly with verifiable
